{"tid":1102684,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"世界上最恐怖嘅感覺！！！","createTime":"2019-04-12T01:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T18:42:28.000Z","uid":217862,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"17f3324c41d829807ecec3b8b33a3ff1a414bbc5","tid":1102684,"uid":217862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T01:43:26.000Z","msg":"就係小學家長日 坐係走廊等入課室見家長嗰陣<br />\n<br />\n小學頭幾年家長日 等入去見班任嗰陣都淆到仆街<br />\n(重有啲急屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n(又係冬天)<br />\n個屎眼差啲頂受唔住 啲屎以攻城門一般嘅撞擊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後我嘅城門都有啲失守，jeeb咗幾滴屎水出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坐住嗰條濕咗嘅底褲長家長<br />\n每一秒都係到挑戰緊自己嘅極限<br />\n見家長嘅不安+屎水底褲嘅挑釁<br />\n少一秒意志都頂受唔住<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n回程返屋企阿媽沿行我後面 不斷以為自己踏狗屎<br />\n(聞到狗屎味&gt;停低check鞋底&gt;睇唔到有狗屎&gt;行幾步&gt;聞到狗屎味)以上過程不斷重複係我地返屋企嘅路途<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企 細佬同老豆係屋企<br />\n我第一時間衝去廁所 拿拿林除咗條吸咗屎水啲底褲出嚟 再放係污衣袋裡面 希望可以瞞天過海<br />\n<br />\n最後就當然比阿媽人屎並獲 罰我一個禮拜唔準屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好奇問阿媽點知係我瀨過屎 唔比係細佬㗎咩<br />\n<br />\n佢答我：我生得你出 點會分唔出你陣屎味 <br />\n<br />\n母親何其偉大阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連我嘅屎味都分得出 定係佢有超能力去分辨屎味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日適逢母親節，不如向自己嘅母親表示愛意 </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉，聽日要見家長<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地都係玩化學實驗 佢屈尻人整化武<br />\n<br />\n唉唔講啦，下個都我啦。"},{"pid":"5064052acd607648d496ffb64c412982157dc656","tid":1102684,"uid":229910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T01:44:56.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"cdac127756c3446a4ffaef66c97ca85c6e333a20","tid":1102684,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T01:45:53.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"b5178796f0665dde1fe6b9d200ae10248762a933","tid":1102684,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T01:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37aa99de6ef68f1ba8294abc555b941f790e101a","tid":1102684,"uid":217862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T01:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d9981e73ce74f23329a0515a224e0030dce465","tid":1102684,"uid":217862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T02:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d845a6a2e6ab39e91ed5cc80e52befc9122db596","tid":1102684,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T02:39:30.000Z","msg":"係寂寞呀！！"},{"pid":"9bcf8713ccfabfc788f38022046da011ebb91480","tid":1102684,"uid":242872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T03:20:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e85a52e0f5ca60ba1f8371e581c1695a4f50e2a","tid":1102684,"uid":15630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:16:49.000Z","msg":"第一次鬼壓床先係最恐怖"},{"pid":"09a2222a7c116cdebb35bc1e333d5c6f574065d7","tid":1102684,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e85a52e0f5ca60ba1f8371e581c1695a4f50e2a","tid":1102684,"uid":15630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:16:49.000Z","msg":"第一次鬼壓床先係最恐怖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:21:30.000Z","msg":"人生第一次比鬼責嚇撚到"},{"pid":"40af47cf13c9bab2875ced6db5464ea41f045d1c","tid":1102684,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T18:33:22.000Z","msg":"DSE考前同DSE放榜前"},{"pid":"2eb9c13f62885003236c90b9d750a720c5fe01b6","tid":1102684,"uid":80243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T18:42:28.000Z","msg":"一個星期冇得屙屎真係完成到？"}]}